    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty ride and it\u2019s been such a joy to drive. It\u2019s in really nice shape and has been super reliable for me. It\u2019s got a few miles of memories but still looks fantastic and runs like a dream! This is the perfect find for someone who wants a dependable, stylish set of wheels that's been well-loved. Come take it for a spin\u2014I'm sure you're going to love it as much as I have!",
      "price": 34500.0,
