      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 36
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E92 M3 is a mechanically sound example of the high-revving S65 platform. The 4.0L naturally aspirated V8 delivers peak torque through a 6-speed longitudinal manual gearbox, paired with a variable M differential lock for superior power delivery out of corners. The chassis features Electronic Damper Control (EDC) and remains structurally rigid with no subframe issues. Recent service includes preventative rod bearing replacement with VAC treated bearings and new throttle actuators to address common S65 failure points. The induction note from the individual throttle bodies is crisp, and the VANOS system operates within factory tolerances. While the finish shows minor road-going patina, the kinematic integrity of the multi-link rear suspension and MacPherson strut front end remains sharp and communicative.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 36
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_9_listing_3",
