    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is powered by the iconic S54 3.2L naturally aspirated inline-six, renowned for its individual throttle bodies and high-revving 8,000 RPM ceiling. Power is sent through a Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox to a factory limited-slip differential, providing exceptional mechanical feedback. The chassis is structurally sound, featuring a reinforced rear subframe and refreshed suspension bushings to maintain optimal turn-in geometry. Recent comprehensive maintenance includes a valve clearance adjustment and a double-VANOS system overhaul, ensuring the variable valve timing remains precise. While the finish shows light road use consistent with its 'good' condition, the drivetrain remains tight and responsive, offering a pure analog driving experience.",
